# Cursor Rules for EvolveAI Project

This file contains project-wide rules for the Cursor AI assistant.

## Project Overview
EvolveAI is a fitness training plan generator with:
- FastAPI backend (Python)
- React Native frontend (TypeScript/Expo)
- Supabase for database and authentication
- OpenAI/Gemini for AI features

## Project-Wide Rules

### Security
- Never commit `.env` files or real API keys
- Always validate JWT tokens for authenticated endpoints
- Don't expose sensitive data in error responses
- Use GitHub Secrets for CI/CD
- Test environment should use dummy values

### Git & Version Control
- Use meaningful commit messages
- Keep commits focused and atomic
- Never commit sensitive data

### Documentation
- Keep README files up to date
- Document complex logic and decisions
- Include examples in documentation

